{"tid":2014948,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【打壓港台】ETV成歷史！政府收回教育電視中心 港台逾百員工及器材須遷出","createTime":"2020-05-13T10:30:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T10:30:21.000Z","uid":135867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7f98eacb01f9fcfd56bfe8d06f6c95afd0628f01","tid":2014948,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T10:30:21.000Z","msg":"【新增教育局回應】<br />\n教育電視（ETV）成為歷史。消息稱，教育局決定收回港台教育電視中心，今天港台將通知有關職員並商討搬遷事宜。據悉，港台管理層通知員工教育局今年9月將會收回該棟大樓，港台的員工及器材都須遷出，預計100多名員工受影響；管理層又指，該局大樓業權屬於教育局，由於局方早前停止與港台製作節目，因此收回相關大樓。<br />\n<br />\n入去睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200513&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60934490\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200513%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60934490&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NQhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=bb71386f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200513%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60934490&h=c0a2e1a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200513&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60934490</a>"}]}